Would be great if possible to isolate code, like for example from:
function name x(){

//code here
}

to the end of the braket by selecting or the function name or defining lines, that would track the function, so we could "hide" all the other code and be able to maybe debug just that bit of code, or style/ reformat / or just because its easier to scroll, or do search and replace.. ( i know the search can be done only on the selected text)  but still it would be nice to "take other functions away from the view". Its more an issue on large files though.
